headline: Best Stock to Buy Right Now: Amazon vs. Home Depot
summary: There's a lot of uncertainty in the stock market right now, and it's causing many investors to reconsider some of their stocks and look at which ones might offer good opportunities to buy.  With U.S. President Donald Trump's ongoing tariff actions against trade partners and some economists increasing their estimates of a potential recession, it's no surprise that investors are taking a more skeptical approach to each stock they buy.  When considering two leading consumer goods companies, Amazon (NASDAQ: AMZN) and Home Depot (NYSE: HD), which looks like the best stock to buy right now?
